Genie AI Service - Detailed Spec

Capabilities

Mode Input Output Use Case
Text Chat "What does my glucose trend mean?" Plain English explanation + recommendations Patient asks about recent data
Voice Spoken question via microphone Text-to-speech response Hands-free, elderly accessibility
Daily Summary Past 24h health data Audio + text summary: "Your glucose was elevated last night..." Morning briefing
Translation Clinical jargon (e.g., "HbA1c 7.2%") Layperson explanation Health literacy
Actionable Insights Symptoms + vitals "You should check ketones and call your doctor" Proactive guidance

API Endpoints

```yaml
# Text Chat
POST /genie/chat
Request:
  {
    "patientId": "uuid",
    "message": "Why is my blood pressure high this week?",
    "context": { "includeRecentData": true }
  }
Response:
  {
    "response": "Based on your last 7 days...",
    "suggestedActions": ["Log sodium intake", "Check medication adherence"],
    "voiceAudioUrl": "https://..."
  }

# Voice (WebSocket)
WS /genie/voice
  → Client sends audio chunks (Opus/WebM)
  ← Server returns streaming text + audio response

# Daily Health Briefing
GET /genie/summary/{patientId}
Response:
  {
    "audioSummary": "Good morning Marcus...",
    "highlights": ["Glucose 215mg/dL at 2am", "Sleep 5.2 hours"],
    "forecast": "Risk of hyperglycemia today: 73%"
  }
```

