Forecast Service - Detailed Spec

Prediction Capabilities

Forecast Type Input Data Output Update Frequency
Glucose (next 24h) Last 14 days CGM, meals, insulin Hourly predictions + confidence intervals Every 30 min
Hypoglycemia risk Current glucose, trend, activity Risk score (0-100) + time-to-event Real-time
Readmission risk Historical, SDOH, med adherence % risk + modifiable factors Daily
BP trend (7d forecast) Daily BP readings, medication Projected values + alert threshold crossing Daily
Sleep pattern Wearable sleep data Predicted sleep quality + recommendations Daily

API Endpoints

```yaml
GET /forecast/glucose/{patientId}
Parameters:
  - hours: 24 (default)
Response:
  {
    "predictions": [
      { "timestamp": "2026-06-13T00:00:00Z", "value": 145, "lower": 120, "upper": 170 },
      { "timestamp": "2026-06-13T02:00:00Z", "value": 160, "lower": 135, "upper": 185 }
    ],
    "riskOfHypoglycemia": 12,
    "riskOfHyperglycemia": 68,
    "recommendations": ["Consider evening snack", "Check before bed"]
